 to feel welcome. I’m very much looking forward to working with colleagues to develop the Island’s breast care service, ensuring that patients receive the highest standard of care possible.”TweetMore from Isle of Man NewsWitnesses sought to bus incidentGas conversion works will force closure of road in CastletownRally Isle of Man set to make 2012 comebackCommentsAdd A CommentLog in to the club to add your comment.NavigationHomeOn AirPresentersScheduleKevin FordGeorge FergusonJason QuinnJamesNJ WilliamsDerek RichardsonClub Classics3FM JukeBox with Athol GarageEasy SundayAdam RussellRon BerryShaun TilleyBen SowreyRichard FaragherPodcastsPhotosPhotosMusicPlaylist SearchPodcastslast.fmListen Live3ODNewsIsle of ManUKWorldShowbiz SkeetVideosSportBusinessStrange BUT True!WebcamsWeatherSurf ReportSchool ClosuresPollIsland InfoAdd an eventAdvertiseAdvertise with 3FMLocal DirectoryContactContact UsFacebookTwitter3FM JobsListenRadioOn 104 to 106 FMiOSDownload our AppAndroidDownload our AppRadioplayerListen Live OnlineExploreHomeOn AirPhotosMusicNewsIsland InfoAdvertiseContactMoreTerms & ConditionsPrivacy PolicyCompetition TermsContact Us© 2012 3FM and G Media